Package: regressionhelper
Type: Package
Title: Implement linear regression method
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kexin Guo
Maintainer: Kexin Guo <kexinguo@umich.edu>
Description: This package includes functions that computing all needed values from a linear regression.
    getBetaHat estimates the coefficients (Beta Hat) of a linear regression model.
    getResidual calculates the residuals of a linear regression model.
    getRsquare calculates the R-Square (coefficient of determination) of a linear regression model.
    getF returns the F-statistic and p-value for a F-test of the linear regression model as a list.
    getT returns T-statistic, standard error, p-value and statistical decision of T-tests for every coefficientin the linear regression model as a list.
